acy and rhythm, while stone and raw wood accents ground the space.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-entryway-100725-944-03.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-entryway-100725-944-03-940x705.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-entryway-100725-944-03-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-entryway-100725-944-03-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-entryway-100725-944-03-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe dining area opens to a modest patio, where meals are set against the backdrop of undisturbed forest. There’s no stark division between indoors and out; instead, the patio and dining space share materials and orientation, allowing gatherings to flow naturally into the landscape.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-open-plan-dining-area-100725-948-01.jpg\" alt=\" Indoor-outdoor dining made effortless. The patio and dining area open directly to the forest, with a shared material palette that connects meals to nature.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-open-plan-dining-area-100725-948-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-open-plan-dining-area-100725-948-01-940x705.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-open-plan-dining-area-100725-948-01-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-open-plan-dining-area-100725-948-01-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-open-plan-dining-area-100725-948-01-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\