pg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-pacific-northwest-house-100725-950-08-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe living room prioritizes views with expanses of windows, and seating oriented toward the fireplace with its steel surround, rather than a screen. Daylight shifts through the space, tracing the sun’s path, bringing softness and warmth to this otherwise rain-heavy region.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-living-room-fireplace-100725-945-03.jpg\" alt=\"The living room prioritizes views with expanses of windows, and seating oriented toward the fireplace with its steel surround, rather than a screen. Daylight shifts through the space, tracing the sun’s path, bringing softness and warmth to this otherwise rain-heavy region.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-living-room-fireplace-100725-945-03.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-living-room-fireplace-100725-945-03-940x705.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-living-room-fireplace-100725-945-03-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-living-room-fireplace-100725-945-03-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-living-room-fireplace-100725-945-03-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-living-room-fireplace-100725-945-02.jpg\" alt=\"The living room prioritizes views with expanses of windows, and seating oriented toward the fireplace with its steel surround, rather than a screen. Daylight shifts through the space, tracing the sun’s path, bringing softness and warmth to this otherwise rain-heavy region.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-living-room-fireplace-100725-945-02.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-living-room-fireplace-100725-945-02-940x705.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-living-room-fireplace-100725-945-02-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-living-room-fireplace-100725-945-02-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-living-room-fireplace-100725-945-02-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-living-room-fireplace-100725-945-04.jpg\" alt=\"The living room prioritizes views with expanses of windows, and seating oriented toward the fireplace with its steel surround, rather than a screen. Daylight shifts through the space, tracing the sun’s path, bringing softness and warmth to this otherwise rain-heavy region.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-living-room-fireplace-100725-945-04.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-living-room-fireplace-100725-945-04-940x705.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-living-room-fireplace-100725-945-04-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-living-room-fireplace-100725-945-04-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-living-room-fireplace-100725-945-04-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe nearby kitchen combines modern clarity with natural warmth. A wood-paneled ceiling adds texture above a streamlined black island and matte fixtures. Open shelving and minimalist cabinetry offer practical storage while keeping the space visually quiet and functional for daily use.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-kitchen-100725-945-01.jpg\" alt=\"This modern kitchen combines modern clarity with natural warmth. A wood-paneled ceiling adds texture above a streamlined black island and matte fixtures. Open shelving and minimalist cabinetry offer practical storage while keeping the space visually quiet and functional for daily use.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-kitchen-100725-945-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-kitchen-100725-945-01-940x705.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-kitchen-100725-945-01-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-kitchen-100725-945-01-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-kitchen-100725-945-01-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eTall windows bring in steady natural light, illuminating the polished concrete floors and pale walls of the music room. Designed for focus and function, the space includes built-in white cabinetry for storage and modern acoustic treatments to support sound clarity. Positioned to face the surrounding forest, the room offers both visual calm and practical quiet, a dedicated space for music without distraction.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-music-room-100715-943-01.jpg\" alt=\"Tall windows bring in steady natural light, illuminating the polished concrete floors and pale walls of the music room. \" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-music-room-100715-943-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-music-room-100715-943-01-940x705.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-music-room-100715-943-01-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-music-room-100715-943-01-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-music-room-100715-943-01-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-music-room-100715-943-02.jpg\" alt=\"Tall windows bring in steady natural light, illuminating the polished concrete floors and pale walls of the music room. \" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-music-room-100715-943-02.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-music-room-100715-943-02-940x705.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-music-room-100715-943-02-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-music-room-100715-943-02-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-music-room-100715-943-02-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eSurrounded by forest and softened by natural light, the bedroom offers a quiet, secluded retreat. Floor-to-ceiling windows frame the trees outside, providing both views and privacy. Simple furnishings and pale bedding keep the space understated, while a warm bedside light adds gentle illumination.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-interior-floor-to-ceiling-windows-100725-940-01.jpg\" alt=\"Surrounded by forest and softened by natural light, the bedroom offers a quiet, secluded retreat. Floor-to-ceiling windows frame the trees outside, providing both views and privacy. Simple furnishings and pale bedding keep the space understated, while a warm bedside light adds gentle illumination.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-interior-floor-to-ceiling-windows-100725-940-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-interior-floor-to-ceiling-windows-100725-940-01-940x705.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-interior-floor-to-ceiling-windows-100725-940-01-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-interior-floor-to-ceiling-windows-100725-940-01-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-interior-floor-to-ceiling-windows-100725-940-01-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-interior-floor-to-ceiling-windows-100725-940-02.jpg\" alt=\"Surrounded by forest and softened by natural light, the bedroom offers a quiet, secluded retreat. Floor-to-ceiling windows frame the trees outside, providing both views and privacy. Simple furnishings and pale bedding keep the space understated, while a warm bedside light adds gentle illumination.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-interior-floor-to-ceiling-windows-100725-940-02.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-interior-floor-to-ceiling-windows-100725-940-02-940x705.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-interior-floor-to-ceiling-windows-100725-940-02-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-interior-floor-to-ceiling-windows-100725-940-02-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-interior-floor-to-ceiling-windows-100725-940-02-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe primary bathroom finds quiet privacy behind an old-growth stump, making the daily act of bathing a moment of intimacy with the forest. Its placement invites occupants to observe the subtle changes in moss, bark, and filtered light, turning a simple ritual into a sensory connection with the land.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-double-vanity-100725-941-01.jpg\" alt=\"The primary bathroom finds quiet privacy behind an old-growth stump, making the daily act of bathing a moment of intimacy with the forest. Its placement invites occupants to observe the subtle changes in moss, bark, and filtered light, turning a simple ritual into a sensory connection with the land.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-double-vanity-100725-941-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-double-vanity-100725-941-01-940x705.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-double-vanity-100725-941-01-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-double-vanity-100725-941-01-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-double-vanity-100725-941-01-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-double-vanity-100725-941-02.jpg\" alt=\"The primary bathroom finds quiet privacy behind an old-growth stump, making the daily act of bathing a moment of intimacy with the forest. Its placement invites occupants to observe the subtle changes in moss, bark, and filtered light, turning a simple ritual into a sensory connection with the land.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-double-vanity-100725-941-02.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-double-vanity-100725-941-02-940x1253.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-double-vanity-100725-941-02-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-double-vanity-100725-941-02-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-double-vanity-100725-941-02-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-double-vanity-100725-941-02-1536x2048.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-double-vanity-100725-941-03.jpg\" alt=\"The primary bathroom finds quiet privacy behind an old-growth stump, making the daily act of bathing a moment of intimacy with the forest. Its placement invites occupants to observe the subtle changes in moss, bark, and filtered light, turning a simple ritual into a sensory connection with the land.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-double-vanity-100725-941-03.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-double-vanity-100725-941-03-940x1253.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-double-vanity-100725-941-03-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-double-vanity-100725-941-03-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-double-vanity-100725-941-03-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-double-vanity-100725-941-03-1536x2048.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eForest Pavilion is a home built not on the land, but with it. A structure that respects the intelligence of the site and the rhythms of life that pass through it. Designed as both refuge and invitation, it allows its occupants to live within the forest, not just beside it.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://niclehoux.com/\"\u003eNic Lehoux\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h6\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
